1
00:01:03,650 --> 00:01:05,870
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:09,730
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:11,110 --> 00:01:13,120
[Spiritual Sound of Stone]

4
00:01:35,870 --> 00:01:37,150
This is...

5
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,789
Mother?

6
00:01:43,430 --> 00:01:45,229
Xingzhi?

7
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:15,400
What brings Your Majesty here?

8
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:17,470
You still owe me an explanation.

9
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,980
Once you explain clearly,

10
00:02:20,470 --> 00:02:21,470
I will leave.

11
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:23,470
There's nothing to explain.

12
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:25,630
We agreed from the beginning

13
00:02:25,910 --> 00:02:29,280
not to ask about each other's past,
only to enjoy our time together.

14
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:32,750
Why must Your Majesty pressure me so?

15
00:02:35,910 --> 00:02:37,910
I am now betrothed to someone.

16
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:44,280
There will be no more
connection between us.

17
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,470
Fine.

18
00:02:57,430 --> 00:02:59,400
Then tell me,

19
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,520
do you truly want to marry that Xun Simo,

20
00:03:02,750 --> 00:03:05,480
or is it the Chunliu Garden
you want as your dowry?

21
00:03:17,550 --> 00:03:18,110
Let's go.

22
00:03:20,410 --> 00:03:22,560
[Spiritual Sound of Stone]

23
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:27,850
[Spiritual Sound of Stone]

24
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:11,760
Your Majesty, please send people
to restore this place,

25
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:13,030
so that the bloodshed

26
00:04:13,030 --> 00:04:15,630
doesn't disturb
my mother's spirit in heaven.

27
00:04:20,360 --> 00:04:21,160
Your Majesty,

28
00:04:21,269 --> 00:04:22,190
today's assassin...

29
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:24,070
It's rather suspicious.

30
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,960
Investigate it thoroughly.

31
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,420
Yes, Your Majesty.

32
00:04:31,070 --> 00:04:31,920
Aunt,

33
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:35,780
I think the ninth day of next month
would be auspicious.

34
00:04:35,830 --> 00:04:38,190
It's better to have the wedding soon.

35
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:42,270
Even so,

36
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:46,750
I still want to arrange
a proper ceremony for you.

37
00:04:46,870 --> 00:04:47,950
Otherwise, how could I face

38
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,870
your father and mother?

39
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:50,750
Aunt.

40
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:51,680
Your Majesty.

41
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:52,870
What is it?

42
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,430
It's fine. Speak.

43
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,800
Your Majesty,

44
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,120
the guards report that

45
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:04,300
His Majesty was attacked by assassins
while traveling incognito today.

46
00:05:04,830 --> 00:05:06,490
Fortunately, he is unharmed.

47
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:09,360
Where did this attack happen?

48
00:05:10,430 --> 00:05:12,630
At a private residence
in the southern city,

49
00:05:12,630 --> 00:05:14,720
called Chunliu Garden.

50
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:17,120
When His Majesty was attacked,

51
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:20,310
Grand Tutor's daughter,
Jiang Li, was also present.

52
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:24,830
Aunt,

53
00:05:24,950 --> 00:05:26,430
I'll go see Miss Jiang.

54
00:05:26,830 --> 00:05:27,690
I take my leave.

55
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,870
Simo.

56
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:34,180
Don't worry, Aunt. I know what I'm doing.

57
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:51,680
My Lady.

58
00:05:52,750 --> 00:05:53,630
My Lady,

59
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:55,720
General Xun has sent someone
to invite you.

60
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:58,310
He wishes to speak with you privately.

61
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,870
Shall we decline?

62
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:06,780
Chunliu Garden is still in his hands.

63
00:06:08,390 --> 00:06:09,720
I'll go and be back soon.

64
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:14,170
[General's Mansion]

65
00:06:16,270 --> 00:06:17,130
Please come in.

66
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,870
Li, I'm surprised
you accepted my invitation

67
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:29,800
to come to my residence so readily.

68
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:33,560
So this is your room?

69
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,390
Please.

70
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,560
I invited you today

71
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,820
mainly because I'm concerned about you.

72
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:46,390
About what happened
at Chunliu Garden today...

73
00:06:46,390 --> 00:06:47,000
This...

74
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,380
Li, you have excellent taste.

75
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:52,630
This is coral from the Treasure Pavilion.

76
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:57,000
This is a green jade inkstone
from Guilin House.

77
00:06:57,000 --> 00:07:00,270
And this is a painted ivory tower.

78
00:07:00,270 --> 00:07:03,600
These treasures are all incredibly rare,

79
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,720
one of a kind in the world.

80
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:06,950
One of a kind?

81
00:07:08,090 --> 00:07:10,730
And you've displayed them
all out like this?

82
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,800
Of course these treasures
should be displayed.

83
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:17,060
That's the only way to honor their value.

84
00:07:17,310 --> 00:07:18,240
Don't you think?

85
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:21,480
I think...

86
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:26,850
it's excellent.

87
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,530
You've been frightened today.

88
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:34,270
Please stay here for the night.

89
00:07:34,630 --> 00:07:37,630
I will certainly protect you well,

90
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,240
never leaving...

91
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,620
What are you doing?

92
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,120
Wait.

93
00:07:43,870 --> 00:07:44,480
Li!

94
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,390
I'm tired.

95
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:47,390
I'll borrow your room for tonight.

96
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:48,390
Please excuse me.

97
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:55,750
Wait.

98
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,870
Since this is Xun Simo's room,

99
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:00,160
then...

100
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:09,720
I'm such a fool.

101
00:08:12,870 --> 00:08:15,730
Even if I find the deed
to Chunliu Garden, what then?

102
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:18,720
I can't just take the garden and run away.

103
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,160
What on earth

104
00:08:22,870 --> 00:08:24,830
should I do?

105
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:54,080
Stop it, Zhao.

106
00:09:01,910 --> 00:09:02,970
What are you doing?

107
00:09:05,150 --> 00:09:06,030
Li,

108
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:09,330
since you've decided to
spend the night at my residence,

109
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:12,610
why pretend
you don't know what's happening?

110
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:14,510
General, you must have
misunderstood something.

111
00:09:14,510 --> 00:09:15,390
I'm leaving.

112
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:20,030
We are betrothed.

113
00:09:20,270 --> 00:09:21,630
It's only a matter of time.

114
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:23,550
Why must you be so reserved?

115
00:09:31,790 --> 00:09:33,390
Do you know how long

116
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,770
I've been waiting for this moment?

117
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,530
-Ge-General.
-Get out!

118
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:51,200
General, His Majesty is here.

119
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,440
I don't care who it is!

120
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,370
What did you say?

121
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:58,080
His Majesty is here. You should go now.

122
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:07,600
Greetings, Your Majesty.

123
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,910
Your Majesty visiting so late at night,

124
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:11,150
may I ask the reason?

125
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,720
Nothing special.

126
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:17,240
I just couldn't sleep

127
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:20,150
and thought I'd play chess with you.

128
00:10:21,270 --> 00:10:22,150
Chess?

129
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:24,720
What? Are you unwilling?

130
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:30,750
Your Majesty, please.

131
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,000
Wait.

132
00:10:37,510 --> 00:10:40,000
Since Li happens to be here,

133
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,200
let her join us.

134
00:10:41,510 --> 00:10:42,870
When playing chess,

135
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:46,240
having someone watch
makes it more enjoyable.

136
00:10:46,630 --> 00:10:49,720
After all, we had an agreement.

137
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:50,840
Didn't we?

138
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:09,550
Guests first. After you, Your Majesty.

139
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:24,150
Although Your Majesty's attack is fierce,

140
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,670
you may not realize

141
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:28,000
that sometimes one should

142
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:29,870
retreat in order to advance.

143
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:36,020
I have played chess since childhood,

144
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:38,010
and I understand one truth:

145
00:11:38,550 --> 00:11:40,550
If you yield at every turn,

146
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:44,200
you will lose the entire board.

147
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:46,670
Indeed.

148
00:11:47,390 --> 00:11:49,480
Your Majesty's power is immense.

149
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,650
How would you know about yielding?

150
00:11:52,030 --> 00:11:54,550
However, your chess strategy

151
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:58,270
might be a bit too aggressive.

152
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:00,670
So what?

153
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:06,440
If you don't defend against this knight,

154
00:12:06,510 --> 00:12:07,840
I'll take it.

155
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:21,080
Checkmate.

156
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,030
General Xun,

157
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,360
it seems

158
00:12:31,750 --> 00:12:33,360
I have won.

159
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,150
It's getting late.

160
00:12:37,390 --> 00:12:39,000
Since the outcome is decided,

161
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,930
please excuse me as I take my leave.

162
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,390
Wait.

163
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:45,360
One game is hardly satisfying.

164
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:49,080
Your Majesty, let's play another round.

165
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:51,870
Since this is a chess match
between you and me,

166
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,670
there's no need

167
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:57,390
to involve Miss Jiang in it.

168
00:12:59,870 --> 00:13:02,000
Your Majesty, what do you mean by that?

169
00:13:03,030 --> 00:13:04,120
Li

170
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:06,390
is my betrothed bride.

171
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:09,080
It's perfectly natural for her

172
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:10,610
to stay and keep me company.

173
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:15,240
What if I simply won't allow it?

174
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:19,670
Report.

175
00:13:19,700 --> 00:13:21,750
[Majestic Presence Descends]

176
00:13:21,750 --> 00:13:24,390
Your Majesty, General Xun,

177
00:13:24,790 --> 00:13:27,910
Her Majesty
summons Miss Jiang to the palace.

178
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:30,670
Me?

179
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:33,630
Why would Aunt summon her so late?

180
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:35,590
Forgive me, I don't know either.

181
00:13:38,510 --> 00:13:39,310
Your Majesty,

182
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:43,080
I'm afraid I must take my leave now.

183
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:45,080
Li, let's go.

184
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:46,390
General Xun,

185
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,630
Her Majesty said

186
00:13:48,630 --> 00:13:50,960
Miss Jiang should enter the palace alone.

187
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:53,600
Miss Jiang, please follow me.

188
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,270
I'm tired.

189
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,120
Let's call it a day.

190
00:14:11,510 --> 00:14:12,310
Your Majesty,

191
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:17,320
I'd like to ask you one question.

192
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,750
Did you

193
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:21,360
truly come to play chess with me tonight?

194
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,320
General Xun,

195
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:35,080
our chess game need not be rushed.

196
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,240
But you'd better think clearly

197
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:40,840
about whether you're the player

198
00:14:41,790 --> 00:14:43,360
or merely a chess piece.

199
00:14:46,050 --> 00:14:47,080
[Majestic Presence Descends]

200
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:49,870
Farewell, Your Majesty.
